[self_consistency][qwen2_5_0_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 33/100 path 3/3 answer='Ray initially had 25 lollipops but kept 5 for himself. So he distributed \\( 25 - 5 = 20 \\) lollipops to his friends. These 20 lollipops were shared equally among his four friends. Therefore, each friend received \\( 20 \\div 4 = 5 \\) lollipops.'
