e part of sales over $1000:\nAdditional commission from above $1000 sales = 10% * ($1000 + $1000) = 10% * $2000 = $200\n\nNow add both parts together to find Antonella's total earnings:\nTotal earnings = Commission from $1000 sales + Additional commission from part over $1000 sales\nTotal earnings = $300 + $200 = $500\n\nSo the amount of money Antonella earned is $500.": 1}
