[self_consistency][qwen2_5_1_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 58/100 path 3/3 answer="First, we calculate how many points Betty collected:\nBetty's points = Adam's points + (Adam's points × 30%)  \n                = 50 + (50 × 0.3)  \n                = 50 + 15  \n                = 65\n\nNext, we determine how many points Tom has:\nTom's points = Betty's points - 30  \n             = 65 - 30  \n             = 35\n\nThen, we find out how many points Marta collected:\nMarta's points = 3 × Tom's points  \n              = 3 × 35  \n              = 105\n\nNow, we sum up all the students' points to see how many points the class has so far:\nTotal points = Adam's points + Betty's points + Marta's points + Tom's points\n            = 50 + 65 + 105 + 35  \n            = 255\n\nTo find out how many points the class still needs to reach the minimum threshold of 400 points, we subtract their current total from the threshold:\nPoints needed = Minimum threshold - Total points\n              = 400 - 255  \n              = 145\n\nTherefore, the class needs 145 more points to go on the trip."
[self_consistency][qwen2_5_1_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 58/100 done id=gsm8k_test_696 prediction='165' gold='145' correct=False vote_counts={'165': 1, '145': 1, "First, we calculate how many points Betty collected:\nBetty's points = Adam's points + (Adam's points × 30%)  \n                = 50 + (50 × 0.3)  \n                = 50 + 15  \n                = 65\n\nNext, we determine how many points Tom has:\nTom's points = Betty's points - 30  \n             = 65 - 30  \n             = 35\n\nThen, we find out how many points Marta collected:\nMarta's points = 3 × Tom's points  \n              = 3 × 35  \n              = 105\n\nNow, we sum up all the students' points to see how many points the class has so far:\nTotal points = Adam's points + Betty's points + Marta's points + Tom's points\n            = 50 + 65 + 105 + 35  \n            = 255\n\nTo find out how many points the class still needs to reach the minimum threshold of 400 points, we subtract their current total from the threshold:\nPoints needed = Minimum threshold - Total points\n              = 400 - 255  \n              = 145\n\nTherefore, the class needs 145 more points to go on the trip.": 1}
